{"tid":1891624,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老末日變天堂】投注站擬下週三重開","createTime":"2020-02-22T03:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T11:12:21.000Z","uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2162cd74b1a3419f54e3dcd08fc03abcd9bd22","tid":1891624,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"因應武漢肺炎疫情持續擴散，兩週前政府曾表示未來兩星期是香港能否控制疫情及防止社區爆發的關鍵時刻，香港賽馬會有鑑於此，當時宣佈將進一步加強預防措施，全港共101間場外投注處將無限期停止服務，直至另行通知。據悉，馬會計畫有意於下週三跑馬地賽事恢復投注站服務。<br />\n<br />\n自從投注站及電話投注（專人接聽）關閉後，馬迷只可用1886自動電話投注系統及網上投注，對不少馬迷造成不便，尤其部分不懂網上投注的年長馬迷，據悉，馬會聽取馬迷的意見及衡量新型冠狀病毒疫情的最新情況後，所以下週三跑馬日恢復投注站服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://racing.appledaily.com.hk/topic/article/7412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fracing.appledaily.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Farticle%2F7412&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=66ca41b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://racing.appledaily.com.hk/topic/article/7412</a>"},{"pid":"86327e3d07d06bc94b86a8ef044fdcfa3c17609c","tid":1891624,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"投胎券幾時復賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48ca27bf449e498da03e690826633e8f712b5fe","tid":1891624,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86327e3d07d06bc94b86a8ef044fdcfa3c17609c","tid":1891624,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"投胎券幾時復賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"唔知喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bd5b3684a0519dcb0a50c8cab2a129499fdb2d","tid":1891624,"uid":323228,"like":2,"d